haversine <- function(lon1,lat1, lon2, lat2) {
  R <- 6371 # 
  dLat <- (lat2 - lat1) * pi / 180
  dLon <- (lon2 - lon1) * pi / 180
  a <- sin(dLat / 2) * sin(dLat / 2) + cos(lat1 * pi / 180) * cos(lat2 * pi / 180) * sin(dLon / 2) * sin(dLon / 2)
  c <- 2 * atan2(sqrt(a), sqrt(1 - a))
  d <- R * c
  return(d)
}
